# SauceDemo: Login and Logout

As a shopper, I want to log in and out successfully.

Acceptance Criteria:
- Using username "standard_user" and password "secret_sauce" logs in.
- After logout, I return to login page.

Base URL: https://www.saucedemo.com/

Gherkin Hints:
Given the login page
When I log in with username "standard_user" and password "secret_sauce"
Then I see "Products"
When I click the menu and logout
Then I return to login page
